    <summary>Additional features for the default GoogleAnalytics module.</summary>
    <description>&lt;p&gt;Additional features for the default GoogleAnalytics module.&lt;p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Current improvements:&lt;p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track every individual page - including sections retrieved via AJAX during one-page-checkout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support for specifying DomainName to use&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track to a secondary profile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track the actual typed in keywords by your customers when bidding on keywords
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optionally track Adwords conversions for purchases
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;First Touch tracking
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Credit for the Keyword Method goes to  Michael Harrison from ROI Revolution (http://www.roirevolution.com/blog/2008/02/exact_keyword_tracking_with_gajs.html)
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    <notes>1.7 compatible, track in different currency</notes>
